 <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">Transmittance spectra in one-dimensional dielectric photonic crystals with defects</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">IOP</subfield>
 </datafield>
 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We have calculated the dependence of transmittance spectra with wavelength for TE wave at normal incidence in one-dimensional dielectric photonic crystals (1DPC) using the transfer matrix method. We demonstrate that when consider two defects layers spatial breaking periodicity in the 1DPC, the presence of defect modes located within the photonic band gap can be found. Additionally we have calculated the effect on the transmittance spectrum by varying the thickness of the defects in the 1DPC.</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">IOP</subfield>
 </datafield>
